comments: Siakam (TOR) firms up and sets the screen on Brogdon (MIL) without delivering contact.
Gasol (TOR) and Antetokounmpo (MIL) engage and disengage during the rebound.
Antetokoumpo (MIL) extends two arms and pushes Leonard (TOR) following the rebound.
VanVleet (TOR) makes incidental "high-five" contact with Bledsoe (MIL) after the release that does not affect his jump shot attempt.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) makes incidental foot to foot contact with Leonard (TOR) in the backcourt.
Brogdon (MIL) makes contact to Leonard's (TOR) arm that affects his driving shot attempt.
Leonard (TOR) makes marginal contact with Middleton (MIL) at the start of his drive that does not affect his SQBR.
Brogdon (MIL) maintains a legal guarding position during the jump shot attempt by Leonard (TOR).
Gasol (TOR) and Lopez (MIL) engage and disengage during the rebound.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) briefly places an arm around Leonard (TOR) but does not affect his ability to get to the rebound.
Lopez (MIL) makes contact with Gasol's (TOR) arm and body, affecting his ability to secure the rebound.
Siakam (TOR) makes incidental contact with Brogdon (MIL) that does not cause him to lose control of the ball.
[Observable in enhanced video] Antetokounmpo (MIL) steps on the sideline and Gasol (TOR) makes brief contact with him with his off-arm before the throw-in is released.

call_type: Turnover: Lost Ball Out of Bounds
comments: After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the floor of Bucks possession is overturned to Raptors possession.  Brogdon (MIL) is the last player to touch the ball before it goes out of bounds.
Lowry (TOR) firms up and sets the screen on Brogdon (MIL) without delivering contact.
VanVleet (TOR) firms up and sets the screen on Brogdon (MIL) without delivering contact.
Middleton (MIL) dislodges Lowry (TOR) and affects his ability to make the pass.
Powell (TOR) maintains a legal guarding position during the jump shot attempt by Middleton (MIL).
Connaughton (MIL) makes incidental contact with VanVleet (TOR) following the rebound.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) commits a take foul on Lowry (TOR).
Lowry (TOR) makes marginal contact with Bledsoe (MIL) on the perimeter that does not affect his SQBR.
